fields.name: A trip around the earth
fields.description: Experience Earth’s wonders from space—from the Great Barrier Reef, Himalayas, Amazon River, and Giza’s Pyramids by day, to the glow of city lights, lightning storms, and the Aurora Borealis by night. Our spacecraft fully orbits the Earth every 90 minutes, making a highly customized flight path possible. Fly over your hometown, famous landmarks and other places meaningful to you.

fields.name: Manta Sleep Mask
fields.description:
If you’ve ever worked with a sleep mask with flimsy straps and a plasticky feel, you know that the wrong sleep mask can be a distraction.

The right sleep mask. Manta’s sleep mask has a seamless, quilted surround that offers cushioning for your whole head, not just your eyes. However, your eyes do get special treatment. With two light-blocking rounded pillows that surround each eye, this sleeping mask comforts without pressure. You have room to softly bat your eyelids as you drift away. There’s no oppressive layer–just the space you need.

The blackout eye mask easily adjusts to fit around any head or hairstyle. Its materials breathe easily. This is no overly warm mask that feels stifling in summer; it’s perfect for year-round sleep support.

fields.name: Clip on Phone Camera Lens
fields.description:
"A 3 in 1 Phone Camera Lens - 0.65x Super wide Angle Lens + 15x MACRO Lens + 230 degree fisheye lens, Meet all you demand on photography. Easy for you to take better photograph and capture the instant beauty on your cell phone. Perfect for capturing breathtaking space picture with your mobile phone.
"

fields.name: Motion sickness pills
fields.description:
These Motion Sickness Pills provides powerful, fast relief from motion sickness when you need it most
Prevents and relieves nausea, dizziness and vomiting
Treats symptoms on the spot.

fields.name: Zero G Pen
fields.description: This Zero Gravity Space Pen has a non-reflective black rubber grip coating. Gebruik makend van de Fisher gasdrukvulling schrijft deze pen op zijn kop, onder elke hoek, onder water, door vet, onder extreme temperaturen, op bijna elke ondergrond, drie keer langer dan een gemiddelde pen en uiteraard in het vacuüm van de ruimte!22

fields.name: Beyond: Visions of the Interplanetary
fields.description: This book has some of the most beautiful planetary photos. The images cover the 8 main planets, and are of exceptional quality. If you're a fan of astronomy and/or planetary science, and enjoy looking at celestial photos, you'll love this book.

fields.name: Our Solar System
fields.description: The universe is huge. With more than 100 billion galaxies and billions of orbiting astronomical bodies, there’s so much to learn. Rocket through the cosmos, and discover everything there is to know about our exciting and mysterious solar system!

fields.name: What makes up the universe?
fields.description: Take a long ride to outer space and discover the universe for what it truly is. Read about stars, planets and galaxies. Discover truths as they're presented through an effective combination of text and visuals. Encourage your child to start reading. Go ahead and grab a copy today.

fields.name: Space Hotel
fields.description:
Can you imagine an international space station having a hotel? Yes, you can now vacation outside Earth. Stay in a one-of-its-kind luxurious hotel. 
With a capacity of 400 people, equipped with restaurants, bars, a gym, a cinema, spa, rooms, and suites.

fields.name: Fly me to the moon
fields.description: Only a people have ever left Earth orbit and journeyed close to the Moon. We will take you to within a few hundred kilometers of the Moon’s surface.  You will see the illuminated far side of the Moon, and then witness the amazing sight of the Earth rising above the surface of the Moon.

fields.name: Levitating Moon Lamp
fields.description: The moon lamp is powered through electromagnetic induction, no need cables or built-in battery. It uses magnetic levitation technique, to suspend and spin automatically in mid-air. Using the most advanced 3D printing technology to precisely reproduce the moon’s surface by high-resolution astronomical data, to create a texture that is very similar to the real moon.

fields.name: Earth with Clouds Globe
fields.description:
The globe utilizes solar technology to rotate silently on its own. It measures 6 inches in diameter.  The globe comes with easy-to-assemble 3-pronged acrylic stand and user manual, all in secure foam packaging.
A unique gift item for home decorators, tech geeks, world travelers, astronomy enthusiasts, educators, and more.  After base assembly, measures approximately 10 inches in height and weighs 6 pounds.

fields.name: Constellation Blanket
fields.description: This constellation blanket is super soft, has all 12 zodiac horoscope star signs/patterns and glows in the dark! All you need to do is put the blanket on a sunny or well lit area for 30 minutes to an hour whenever the glow-in-the-dark starts to dim and it should be fully recharged!

fields.name: Monopoly Night Sky
fields.description: The night sky edition is the perfect introduction to a lifetime of cosmic exploration and enjoyment. It comes complete with 6 collectible pewter tokens meade telescope, radio telescope, hubble space telescope, observatory, meade binoculars and mars rover.

fields.name: A space walk
fields.description: A spacewalk is one of the pinnacles of human spaceflight. Even for professional astronauts, the opportunity to leave the space station and float above the Earth is a rare and exhilarating experience.

fields.name: Space Station ISS
fields.description:
The International Space Station (ISS) is mankind’s only permanently manned outpost. In low-Earth orbit it circles the Earth every 90 minutes.
A visit to the ISS is like no other experience.  When you reach Earth orbit you will be traveling at 17,500 miles per hour, over 250 miles above the Earth’s surface and you will be weightless, floating inside your spacecraft.

fields.name: A trip to mars
fields.description: At an average distance of 140 million miles, Mars is one of Earth's closest habitable neighbors.

fields.name: Wireless headphones
fields.description: These headphones have outstanding sound quality and satisfaction is our paramount goal. High definition stereo headphones together with advanced software and noise reduction technology are designed to reduce ambient noises. It is ideal for phone calls, music, and entertainment. Lose yourself in immersive music even in the lowest volume levels!

fields.name: Astronomy Binoculars
fields.description:
"Multi coated optics with a large aperture perfect for low light conditions and stargazing. Diopter adjustment for fine focusing; Angular field of view 4.4 degrees.
A large 70 millimeter objective lens offers maximum image brightness in low light and long range conditions."
